*Lica* su se smejala do suza. (The faces were laughing until they were in tears.)

*Lica* su mu postala bleda. (His face became pale.)

*Lica* su se zbunjeno okrenula prema njemu. (The faces turned confusedly towards him.)

*Licima* je bilo teško da se suoče sa ovim. (It was hard for them to face this.)

*Lice* joj je bilo puno radosti. (Her face was full of joy.)

*Lica* su se osunčala pod suncem. (The faces shone in the sun.)